                            <comment id="417033" author="adilger" created="Fri, 7 Jun 2024 22:57:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like this is hitting the same issue as &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16623&quot; title=&quot;lod_statfs_and_check() does not skip unusable OSTs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-16623&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-16623&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, where a full-width striping is short one OST occasionally:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;lfs migrate:  
-E 1048576 -c 1 -S 524288 -L raid0 -E 2097152 -c 2 -S 524288 -L raid0 -E 3145728 -c 2 -S 524288 -L raid0 -E -1 -c 7 -S 524288 -L raid0 !=
-E 1048576 -c 1 -S 524288 -L raid0 -E 2097152 -c 2 -S 524288 -L raid0 -E 3145728 -c 2 -S 524288 -L raid0 -E -1 -c 6 -S 524288 -L raid0 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;note &quot;&lt;tt&gt;-c &lt;b&gt;7&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; vs. &quot;&lt;tt&gt;-c &lt;b&gt;6&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; in the last component.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Probably a similar fix as patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/54778&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/54778&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16623&quot; title=&quot;lod_statfs_and_check() does not skip unusable OSTs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-16623&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-16623&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; tests: ignore sanity-pfl stripe-count off-by-1&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; is needed, probably by converting &lt;tt&gt;test_56xe&lt;/tt&gt; to use a helper function like &lt;tt&gt;verify_comp_attr()&lt;/tt&gt; or similar.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
